      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape for its next owner. It drives beautifully and has been well-loved, so you\u2019re getting a great ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road immediately. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with everything it needs. If you're looking for a dependable set of wheels without breaking the bank, this is the one! Drop me a message if you have any questions at all\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 31500.0,
