    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, known for its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional tactile feedback and power delivery. The chassis has been vetted for subframe integrity, with upgraded bushings to maintain the precision of the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Recent technical service includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh using OEM components. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the structural and mechanical vitals remain sharp, offering a pure analog performance experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
